  HOMEPAGE='http://search.cpan.org/search?dist=TimeDate'
       REQ='perl'
  ESTIMATE='50'
  EPROVIDE='DateManip perl--DateManip'
      DESC='perl--Date-Manip is a perl module for easily parsing and manipulating dates
Date::Manip is a perl module which allows
for easily parsing and manipulate dates
(several different foreign languages are supported
and more can be added easily,
international date formats are also supported).
A date calculator is also included to tell the
time elapsed between two dates, or to find a
date a certain amount of time from a given date.
Calculations can also be done using a special
business mode where weekends and holidays are ignored.'
